// TypeScript readonly与const区别文章页面
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>TypeScript中的readonly与const的区别是什么</title>
    
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
        max-width: 900px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
